word_mean_info__list.difference: 指时间或空间的延长，也可指影响和使用范围等的扩大。

bilingual.source: We need to extend the meeting time.
bilingual.target: 我们需要延长会议时间。

bilingual.source: We plan to extend our business hours.
bilingual.target: 我们计划延长营业时间。

bilingual.source: We need to extend the contract period.
bilingual.target: 我们需要延长合同期限。

bilingual.source: Can you extend your stay for another week?
bilingual.target: 你能把你的逗留时间延长一周吗？

bilingual.source: The doctor advised him to extend his recovery period.
bilingual.target: 医生建议他延长康复期。

bilingual.source: Refrigeration can extend the shelf life of food.
bilingual.target: 冷藏可以延长食品的保质期。

bilingual.source: The creditor agreed to extend the repayment period.
bilingual.target: 这个贷方同意延长还款期限。

bilingual.source: Can you extend the deadline for this project?
bilingual.target: 你可以延长这个项目的截止日期吗？

bilingual.source: You can extend the warranty for an additional fee.
bilingual.target: 你可以支付额外费用延长保修。

yingyinNormal.en: He says he can reopen and extend the voting day into tomorrow. Tell him it's not safe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他说他可以重开选站将投票日延长到明天。告诉他这不安全。

yingyinNormal.en: The Aquascum 2003 is an all-purpose, self-cleaning maintenance-free, salt-water purifier that is guaranteed to extend the life of your aquarium fish.
yingyinNormal.zh: 水得清具有自动清洁免于维护污水过滤等功能，保证大大延长你水族箱里的鱼的寿命。

yingyinNormal.en: And, since you didn't exercise your right to revoke, I exercised my right to extend, triggering this long-form rental agreement, of which you're already in violation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 既然你没有行使废除合约的权利，我就行使我的权利来延长合约，这份超详细的租赁合同现在生效，而你已经违反了上面的条约。

yingyinNormal.en: I hope you will extend my warm thoughts to Mrs. Underwood. I certainly will.
yingyinNormal.zh: 希望代我转达对安德伍德夫人的问候。我会的。

yingyinNormal.en: Go as my envoy to Sidao. Extend an invitation for parley on the eve of his defeat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你去作为我的使者见见贾似道，在打败他的前夕邀请他和谈。

yingyinNormal.en: Will the coverage extend to Jason? No, he's a freelancer. I don't think it's a problem.
yingyinNormal.zh: 能延伸支付杰森的保险吗？不行，他是自由职业者，我不知道还要考虑他。

yingyinNormal.en: This is the moment to extend your divine influence, to honor the memory of the late Emperor and strengthen the morale of your officers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 诚宜开张圣听，以光先帝遗德，恢弘志士之气，

yingyinNormal.en: And so, what I did was I simply ask our viewers, do what you can, wherever you are, from wherever you sit in life, giving your time, or your talent, your money if you have it, and they did, extend yourself in kindness to other human beings wherever you can.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我所做的仅仅是号召我们的观众尽己所能，无论地域与地位，如果可能，请拿出你们的时间，智慧与财力，他们也的确鼎力相助，无论你在哪里，请为他人送去自己的仁爱之心。

yingyinNormal.en: So, in the interest of authenticity, DW Preminger's going to extend an invitation to the real life friends of his daughter's imagination because what could be more Hollywood authentic than holding out false hope to you, who inspired the roles, to audition for the roles, of Dookas. Dookas? Zed. Zed?
yingyinNormal.zh: 既然你们对真实性感兴趣，就让DW·普雷明格邀请我女儿现实生活中的朋友参演她创作的这部电影，没什么比虚假的希望更符合好莱坞了……所以请你们来试镜，你们正是这些角色的灵感来源，杜卡斯……杜卡斯？泽德……泽德？

exam_freq_info.chinese: 延伸; 伸展; 扩展; 适用于

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The demand that rose in those societies for entry to higher education <highlight>extended</highlight> to groups and social classes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些社会对进入高等教育的需求增加，并扩大到群体和社会阶层。

examination_example.sentence: To find out if this <highlight>extends</highlight> to non-living beings, they tested whether rats can detect social signals from robotic rats.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为了弄清楚这是否延伸到非生物身上，他们测试了老鼠是否能检测到机器人老鼠发出的社会信号。

examination_example.sentence: The Vermont case will offer a precedent-setting test of how far those powers <highlight>extend</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 佛蒙特州的案件将为这些权力的延伸提供一个先例。

examination_example.sentence: 5bn programme of grants to fund new affordable housing is unlikely to be <highlight>extended</highlight> beyond then.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 50亿英镑的新经济适用房资助计划不太可能延续到那个时候之后。

examination_example.sentence: But they certainly will reshape it, and all the more so the longer they <highlight>extend</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但他们肯定会重塑它，而且延续时间越长越是如此。
